{"tid":1349647,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯上周「獻計」鄉事：「密啲手，將佢打到去片甲不留」","createTime":"2019-07-22T10:48:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T06:59:39.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8d45749bc17e28a928aaa7dd968cf0eb69154cf1","tid":1349647,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:48:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190722/large/1563783967_3c16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190722%2Flarge%2F1563783967_3c16.jpg&h=7dbe67cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n元朗昨晚（21日）有大批白衣人毆打無辜市民，立法會議員何君堯被拍到與白衣人握手，他今日（22日）開記者會否認策劃事件，惟《蘋果》發現他早於上周已公然「獻計」，指若有反送中示威者去元朗，建議鄉事派「密啲手，將佢打到去片甲不留」，更建議鄉議局動員18區「民團」成立「機動部隊」，到不同地方「支援」。<br />\n<br />\n翻查何君堯facebook影片紀錄，他於上周一（15日）進行Facebook直播，他在直播開始就譴責近日反送中運動示威者，包括上水及沙田兩次的衝突，稱其為暴徒，形容示威者兇殘、嗜血，他指香港社會不應向「黑勢力」、「恐怖主義」妥協，否則香港「就會玩完」。<br />\n<br />\n其後，他在影片表現「歡迎」示威者到元朗，「元朗我歡迎佢哋嚟，嚟到會點呀？會招呼佢哋」，他形容元朗27鄉「重兵」，若示威者到元朗，鄉事派必定有所「作為」，「我對我哋元朗六鄉嘅係非常之有信心，佢哋多多嚟，你就密啲手，將佢打到去片甲不留。」<br />\n<br />\n何君堯指自己不害怕「黃絲」批評，「呢個就係我要獻嘅計，要同各個板塊聯繫起來」，他進一步「獻計」，建議鄉議局號召18區「民團」，成立一隊4人的機動部隊，若任何一區有示威活動，就派出機動部隊支援，「一方有難，十八方支援。」<br />\n<br />\n何君堯又形容近日反送中運動有「四害」，包括是記者、泛民議員、教協及在示威地區唱聖詩的教徒，他指警方在執法時，對記者及泛民議員毋須手軟，「叫佢哋全部行開，唔係就全部逮捕」；而教協同教徒，他就恐嚇指「你哋兩批人最好做返自己應該做嘅嘢，「如果唔係我就ha到你去lujah。」<br />\n<br />\n警方近日執法濫用暴力備受批評，何君堯卻認為警方過份克制，「唔洗畀面任何人，行埋去就噍佢哋，最低嘅武力高少少都得」，呼籲警方執法時使用更多武力，「一係你死，一係佢死，絕對唔能夠攬炒。」"},{"pid":"2c0117fa1c60123ee8ac9d8aed8ae8f428a64263","tid":1349647,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:48:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190722/59850694\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190722%2F59850694&d=xXKwZA8amEcq1HGFygGyKi6Ol0HYJA13lVA%2BPgi6hPY%3D&h=a282ea76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190722%2F59850694&h=06626ebd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190722/59850694</a>"},{"pid":"81e57c09d31afaac02a0d855e5dcdc01304d6d1d","tid":1349647,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0c7ce5d6e2fa5da881c3056b5846507246382f6","tid":1349647,"uid":45830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:53:44.000Z","msg":"佢叻仔黎架"},{"pid":"f0699a27d5a9a5cfe37719e6f9f0628e1b189ea3","tid":1349647,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:57:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89bf6e534e78df545596ccef98265fd3d0af05e3","tid":1349647,"uid":52962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:00:47.000Z","msg":"「呢個就係我要獻嘅計，要同各個板塊聯繫起來」<br />\n<br />\n做到了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318ec51f08afa61e356edec1e1e90e265e06f41a","tid":1349647,"uid":147017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T04:29:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f6764b66365757bbab379cb97d5e8d3d769813","tid":1349647,"uid":147017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T05:16:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16bc9900b15b8b333631dbef4d26d481335fd05d","tid":1349647,"uid":147017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T05:30:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb1513c2586860c1cedc941474c289a664eeaf34","tid":1349647,"uid":147017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T05:58:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid